-----------------------------------------------
|0 |SORT                             |        |
|1 |└─SUBPLAN FILTER                 |        |
|2 |  ├─PX COORDINATOR               |        |
|3 |  │ └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR         |:EX10000|
|4 |  │   └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR    |        |
|5 |  │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN        |lyq_test|
|6 |  └─LIMIT                        |        |
|7 |    └─PX COORDINATOR             |        |
|8 |      └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR       |:EX20000|
|9 |        └─LIMIT                  |        |
|10|          └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR|        |
|11|            └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |lyq_test|
===============================================
